Class QueryResultIMPL

java.lang.Object
implementation.QueryResultIMPL
All Implemented Interfaces:
fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.QueryResultI, Serializable
public class QueryResultIMPL extends Object implements fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.QueryResultI

Description

The class QueryResultIMPL acts as the implementation of the QueryResultI interface. It is used to store the result of a query.
